This can be done using a Nix OS installation: nix-build -A iso\_minimal
/etc/nixos/nixos/release.nix

Software on the CDROM image can be extended or changed according to the
rules for a normal Nix OS installation, see [install/remove
software](//Install/remove software)

Without NixOS you need to supply the
[source](https://svn.nixos.org/repos/nix/nixos/trunk/) instead of
/etc/nixos/nixos.

See also section "Building your own NixOS CD" of the [NixOS
manual](http://hydra.nixos.org/job/nixos/trunk/manual/latest/download).

